The '''''Tradewyn''''' was the [[Mon Calamari Star Cruiser/Legends|Mon Calamari Star Cruiser]] [[Flagship/Legends|flagship]] of [[Bornaryn Trading]], and the home of the [[House of Thul|Thul family]] after the [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|destruction of Alderaan]]. [[Raynar Thul]] was born on the ''Tradewyn'' circa [[9 ABY/Legends|9 ABY]].

